<html><head></head><body dir=3D"auto" style=3D"overflow-wrap: =
break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; line-break: =
after-white-space;">Kia Ora, Grant,<br><div><p data-start=3D"313" =
data-end=3D"677">On&nbsp;<span data-start=3D"316" data-end=3D"331">1 =
July 2025</span>&nbsp;I requested a copy of my full claim file under =
the&nbsp;<span data-start=3D"383" data-end=3D"403">Privacy Act =
2020</span>&nbsp;(including assessments, communications, and =
inventories). I understand Tower is required to provide this within 20 =
working days, which has now passed. Could you please update me on the =
progress of my request, or confirm if I should direct this to Tower=E2=80=99=
s Privacy Officer?</p><p data-start=3D"679" data-end=3D"955">In =
addition, given that the claim is still progressing, I would appreciate =
it if Tower could provide me with&nbsp;<span data-start=3D"788" =
data-end=3D"856">updated copies of my full claim file on at least a =
monthly basis</span>. This will help ensure accuracy and transparency as =
new assessments and documents are generated.</p><p data-start=3D"957" =
data-end=3D"1088">I value your assistance on this matter and would =
prefer to resolve it directly with your help. Please let me know the =
next steps.</p><p data-start=3D"1090" data-end=3D"1144">Ng=C4=81 =
mihi,</p><p data-start=3D"1090" =
data-end=3D"1144">Raffae</p></div><div><div =
class=3D"AppleOriginalContents" style=3D"direction: =
ltr;"><br><blockquote type=3D"cite"><div>On 1 Jul 2025, at 11:31=E2=80=AFP=
M, Raffaella del Prete &lt;raffaellanz@icloud.com&gt; wrote:</div><br =
class=3D"Apple-interchange-newline"><div><meta http-equiv=3D"content-type"=
 content=3D"text/html; charset=3Dutf-8"><div style=3D"overflow-wrap: =
break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; line-break: after-white-space;"><p =
data-start=3D"302" data-end=3D"323">Hi Sasha &nbsp;and Chris,</p><p =
data-start=3D"325" data-end=3D"528">I saw that you've recently tried to =
get in touch earlier today, unfortunately I was unable to attend your =
calls.. For clarity and consistency, can we please have &nbsp;all =
communication from this point forward be conducted&nbsp;<strong =
data-start=3D"470" data-end=3D"487">by email only</strong>?&nbsp;</p><p =
data-start=3D"530" data-end=3D"581">I would appreciate your attention to =
the following:</p><ol data-start=3D"583" data-end=3D"1781"><li =
data-start=3D"583" data-end=3D"875"><p data-start=3D"586" =
data-end=3D"702"><strong data-start=3D"586" data-end=3D"621">Claim =
Updates and Forward Plan:</strong><br data-start=3D"621" =
data-end=3D"624">Could you elease provide a current update and clear =
next steps for both of my claims:&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"708" =
data-end=3D"729">House (C90306048) and&nbsp;</strong><strong =
data-start=3D"737" data-end=3D"761">Contents (C90306256.</strong>This =
should include any scopes of work, contractor involvement, decisions =
pending, and expected timeframes.&nbsp;</p><p data-start=3D"586" =
data-end=3D"702">Also can we agree that you will send updates on both =
every week so that we can ensure alignment and progress?</p></li><li =
data-start=3D"877" data-end=3D"1200"><p data-start=3D"880" =
data-end=3D"1200"><strong data-start=3D"880" data-end=3D"923">Privacy =
Act Request =E2=80=93 Full Claim Files:</strong><br data-start=3D"923" =
data-end=3D"926">Under the&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"939" =
data-end=3D"959">Privacy Act 2020</strong>, I formally request =
a&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"982" data-end=3D"1006">full copy of my =
file</strong>&nbsp;for both claims (<span data-start=3D"708" =
data-end=3D"729">C90306048 and&nbsp;</span><span data-start=3D"737" =
data-end=3D"761">C90306256</span><span data-start=3D"737" =
data-end=3D"761">)</span>. This includes all internal notes, reports, =
third-party correspondence, scopes, assessments, emails, and any other =
material Tower holds in relation to these claims.</p></li><li =
data-start=3D"1202" data-end=3D"1549"><p data-start=3D"1205" =
data-end=3D"1549"><strong data-start=3D"1205" data-end=3D"1256">Claims =
Preparation Costs &amp; Structural Engineer:</strong><br =
data-start=3D"1256" data-end=3D"1259">I would like to engage =
a&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"1317" data-end=3D"1340">structural =
engineer</strong>&nbsp;to assist with damage assessment. Please confirm =
whether Tower requires prior approval of this engagement, and provide =
the&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"1464" data-end=3D"1499">policy guidelines =
or procedures</strong>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"1504" =
data-end=3D"1548">reimbursement of claims preparation =
work</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=3D"1551" data-end=3D"1781"><p =
data-start=3D"1554" data-end=3D"1781"><strong data-start=3D"1554" =
data-end=3D"1584">Outstanding Expense Claim:</strong><br =
data-start=3D"1584" data-end=3D"1587">I submitted an expense claim =
on&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"1622" data-end=3D"1633">26 June</strong>, =
and I=E2=80=99ve not yet received any update or confirmation. Please =
advise on the status of this claim and when I can expect a response or =
reimbursement.</p></li></ol><p data-start=3D"1783" data-end=3D"1868">Kind =
regards,</p><p data-start=3D"1870" data-end=3D"1909"><strong =
data-start=3D"1886" data-end=3D"1909">Raffaella Del =
Prete</strong></p></div></div></blockquote></div><br></div></body></html>=

